1724
01:55:09,821 --> 01:55:13,616
And you would describe Mr. Jensen's
position on Beale as inflexible?

1725
01:55:14,117 --> 01:55:16,619
Intractable and adamantine.

1726
01:55:18,497 --> 01:55:21,665
So, what do we do
about this Beale son of a bitch?

1727
01:55:23,835 --> 01:55:25,920
