1751
01:56:56,469 --> 01:56:59,013
The network can't be implicated.

1752
01:57:09,524 --> 01:57:13,736
I hope you don't have any hidden
tape machines in this office, Frank.

1753
01:57:15,864 --> 01:57:18,741
Well, the issue is,
shall we kill Howard Beale or not?

1754
01:57:18,909 --> 01:57:21,368
I'd like to hear some more opinions on that.

1755
01:57:21,536 --> 01:57:24,955
I don't see we have any option, Frank.
Let's kill the son of a bitch.

1756
01:57:25,207 --> 01:57:28,584
Ladies and gentlemen, let's hear it.
